      <title>纽约社区银行任命新执行主席</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/new-york-community-bancorp-names-new-executive-chair-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的银行纽约社区银行 (New York Community Bancorp) 周三任命银行业资深人士亚历山德罗·迪内洛 (Alessandro DiNello) 为董事长，该银行业资深人士在该银行 2022 年收购 Flagstar Bank 后加入其董事会，立即生效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/new-york-community-bancorp-names-new-executive-chair-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:27:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
