      <title>美国加强国家烟尘标准和行业目标</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/us-strengthens-national-soot-standards-industry-objects-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府周三十多年来首次加强了烟尘空气质量标准，预计将带来 460 亿美元的健康效益，同时行业团体警告此举将损害一些当地经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/us-strengthens-national-soot-standards-industry-objects-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:11:44 GMT</pubDate>
