      <title>Roblox 预测 2024 年预订量强劲；假期期间游戏内支出大幅增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/roblox-forecasts-strong-2024-bookings-in-game-spending-gets-holiday-boost-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[游戏平台 Roblox 周三预计年度预订量将高于预期，因假期期间游戏内支出增加，其季度预订量首次突破 10 亿美元，导致其股价在盘前上涨 15%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/roblox-forecasts-strong-2024-bookings-in-game-spending-gets-holiday-boost-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:07:43 GMT</pubDate>
