      <title>肯德基母公司百胜餐饮集团的销售受到消费者谨慎支出的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/kfc-parent-yum-brands-misses-sales-estimates-amid-cautious-consumer-spending-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，百胜餐饮集团的季度销售额低于华尔街预期，其三大顶级连锁店的增长均较弱，因为在美国消费环境波动的情况下，塔可钟、肯德基和必胜客的顾客数量减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/kfc-parent-yum-brands-misses-sales-estimates-amid-cautious-consumer-spending-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:07:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
